{"tid":1430975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"改基本法咁大鑊，但冇人講！","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:25:51.000Z","uid":51652,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9750f71705f3e2669ccb57322a8183cf38825a64","tid":1430975,"uid":51652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"最新一期《壹週刊》報道指，政府的《基本法》簡介刪去了「香港居民不受任意或非法逮捕、拘留、監禁。禁止任意或非法搜查居民的身體、剝奪或限制居民的人身自由」一段。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，由於《基本法》原文長達110頁，一般人未必花時間詳閱，故政府過去一直會製作兩頁紙、約3800字簡介，政府網站、《基本法》網站、中學通識科課程等都有使用。<br />\n<br />\n不過報道發現，今年12月新修訂的簡介，把2007年版本中引述的《基本法》第28條，即「香港居民不受任意或非法逮捕、拘留、監禁。禁止任意或非法搜查居民的身體、剝奪或限制居民的人身自由」，全段刪去。<br />\n<br />\n新版本簡介還修改了「一國兩制」、「高度自治」、「港人治港」的排序，把「高度自治」由第二改成第三，並把引號（「」）除去。此外，新版本把香港行政機關及立法機關組成，以及特區自行處理有關的對外事務等條文，紛紛加上「人大授權及依照《基本法》有關規定組成」等字眼，凸出人大憲制角色。<br />\n<br />\n曾任基本法起草委員會的民主黨創黨主席李柱銘直言，有關改動估計與國務院早前發表的《一國兩制》白皮書有關，明顯緊跟中央路線，認為政府應該解釋。<br />\n<br />\n香港通識教育聯會主席許承恩指，看完新版本簡介，不認為政府出的教材便「100%絕對中立」，建議政府製作有關小冊子時，加入原文讓公眾自行對比及判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20141223/s00001/1419323805867/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B%E5%88%AA%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%88%96%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%80%AE%E6%8D%95%E3%80%8D%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87?fbclid=IwAR3jrcZkFR77UdT3RB_PvLpxvqwAGbfCmEGXLdVoiiD9TSaKE6c-4yeCqfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141223%2Fs00001%2F1419323805867%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2588%25AA%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2580%25AE%25E6%258D%2595%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%2587%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3jrcZkFR77UdT3RB_PvLpxvqwAGbfCmEGXLdVoiiD9TSaKE6c-4yeCqfo&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJYV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=4e09a75c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141223%2Fs00001%2F1419323805867%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2588%25AA%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2580%25AE%25E6%258D%2595%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%2596%2587%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3jrcZkFR77UdT3RB_PvLpxvqwAGbfCmEGXLdVoiiD9TSaKE6c-4yeCqfo&h=90dec8be\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20141223/s00001/1419323805867/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%B3%95%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B%E5%88%AA%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%88%96%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%80%AE%E6%8D%95%E3%80%8D%E6%A2%9D%E6%96%87?fbclid=IwAR3jrcZkFR77UdT3RB_PvLpxvqwAGbfCmEGXLdVoiiD9TSaKE6c-4yeCqfo</a>"},{"pid":"779428d8b3616e7c240966b80cc953106973702e","tid":1430975,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"037415d0ca3721f4d21352fc5cb707c9c97e2f80","tid":1430975,"uid":42982,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:26:00.000Z","msg":"舊聞，唔係話唔重要，但目前集中咗最新事態發展先。"},{"pid":"a3af81ecf3ca22a1b465d50106a9cd70b29165ce","tid":1430975,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"改簡介"},{"pid":"9e00faa5e03ca6f95e77b2fd19556d25fb7f94c7","tid":1430975,"uid":47647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"借位一用8月8日取消海港城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KErogZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKErogZ1.jpg&h=6de0a0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPyaGrG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPyaGrG.jpg&h=4fe267a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhYJ1rG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum